message:
feat(browser): Add IndexedDB + OPFS storage for local datasets

- Add DatasetStorage class for persisting Lance files locally
- Small files (<50MB) stored in IndexedDB
- Large files (>=50MB) stored in OPFS (Origin Private File System)
- Auto-detect storage backend, fallback to IndexedDB if OPFS unavailable
- Add list/delete/exists/getUsage APIs for dataset management
- Export datasetStorage global instance and DatasetStorage class
- Add TypeScript definitions for storage APIs

Usage:
  import { datasetStorage } from '@lanceql/browser';

  // Save uploaded file
  await datasetStorage.save('my-dataset', fileBuffer);

  // Load later (persists across sessions)
  const data = await datasetStorage.load('my-dataset');

  // List all saved datasets
  const datasets = await datasetStorage.list();

